sql_statement.static: Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'FrameSize', CASE WHEN Sb.FpsLoad < 0 THEN 0.00 ELSE ROUND(Sb.FpsLoad-0.005,2) END AS 'FPS', Sb.PercentageLoad AS 'Load', Sb.BpsLoad AS 'BpsLoad', Sb.MbpsLoad AS 'MbpsLoad', RxRes.DroppedFrameCount AS 'DroppedCount', RxRes.ReorderedFrameCount AS 'ReorderedCount', RxRes.DuplicateFrameCount AS 'DuplicateCount', Sb.PercentageLoad AS 'MaxRate', RxRes.FrameCount AS 'RxFrameCount', TxRes.FrameCount as 'TxFrameCount', ((((RxRes.L1BitCount / 1000000.0) / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) / ((Sb.MbpsLoad * 100.0) / Sb.PercentageLoad)) * 100.0) AS 'RxLoad', (RxRes.FrameCount / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) AS 'RxFPS', ((Sb.MbpsLoad * 100.0) / Sb.PercentageLoad) AS 'LineSpeed', (SELECT Port.Location FROM Port WHERE Port.Handle = TxRes.ParentHnd) AS 'TxPort', (SELECT Port.Location FROM Port WHERE Port.Handle = RxRes.ParentHnd) AS 'RxPort', (SELECT Port.Name FROM Port WHERE Port.Handle = TxRes.ParentHnd) AS 'TxPortName', (SELECT Port.Name FROM Port WHERE Port.Handle = RxRes.ParentHnd) AS 'RxPortName' From RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb JOIN Analyzer as ana JOIN AnalyzerPortResults as anaRes ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock  = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle and anaRes.ParentHnd = ana.Handle AND  ana.ParentHnd = RxRes.ParentHnd

SELECT IterationNum as 'IterationNum', FrameSize AS 'FrameSize', sum(case when TxPortName like 'West Port Group%' then FPS else 0 end) as 'FPS', Load as 'Load', BpsLoad as 'BpsLoad', MbpsLoad as 'MbpsLoad', sum(case when RxPortName like 'East Port Group%' then DroppedCount else 0 end) as 'DroppedCount' , sum(case when RxPortName like 'East Port Group%' then ReorderedCount else 0 end) as 'ReorderedCount' , sum(case when RxPortName like 'East Port Group%' then ReorderedCount else 0 end) as 'DuplicateCount' , MaxRate as 'MaxRate', sum(case when TxPortName like 'West Port Group%' then TxFrameCount else 0 end) as 'TxFrameCount', sum(case when RxPortName like 'East Port Group%' then RxFrameCount else 0 end) as 'RxFrameCount' , SUM(case when RxPortName like 'East Port Group%' then round(RxLoad,2) else 0 end ) / (select StreamCount from StreamCountConfig  where side like 'East%') AS 'RxLoad', sum(case when RxPortName like 'East Port Group%' then RxFPS else 0 end) as 'RxFPS' , cast(LineSpeed as int) AS 'LineSpeed' From MethRfc2889MaxForwardingIterations GROUP BY FrameSize, IterationNum, Load order by IterationNum
